  <body>
    <h1>Lemonade</h1>
    <p>Lemonade is a drink made from lemon juice, water, and sugar</p>
    <img src="" alt="Picture of Lemonade">
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>4 to 5 large lemons</li>
      <li>1 cup sugar</li>
      <li>1 liter of water</li>
      <li>ice</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Instructions</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Slice the lemons in half</li>
      <li>Squeeze them into a large measuring cup</li>
      <li>Remove any seeds</li>
      <li>Combine the lemon juice and sugar</li>
      <li>Stir into water</li>
      <li>Serve over ice</li>
      <li>Enjoy</li>
    </ol>
  </body>

</html>
